  "name": "Progenitor's Sting",
  "permission": {
    "default": 0
  },
  "type": "feat",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can magically apply your toxic essence onto your weapon or onto the weapon of a willing ally within 30 feet as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Standard-Actions\">standard action</a>. (Poison—injury;&nbsp;save&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Fortitude\">Fort</a>&nbsp;DC 10 + half your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/sorcerer\">sorcerer</a>&nbsp;level + your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Charisma-Cha-\">Charisma</a>&nbsp;modifier;&nbsp;frequency&nbsp;1/round for 6 rounds;&nbsp;effect&nbsp;1&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Strength-Str-\">Str</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Dexterity-Dex-\">Dex</a>, or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Constitution-Con-\">Con</a>&nbsp;damage [chosen when this ability is used];&nbsp;cure&nbsp;1 save).</p>\n<p>You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Charisma-Cha-\">Charisma</a>&nbsp;modifier.</p>\n<p>At 5th level, the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Ability-Score-Damage\">ability damage</a>&nbsp;of your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/afflictions/poison\">poison</a>&nbsp;increases to 1d3.</p>\n<p>At 7th level, each time you apply your progenitor’s sting, you can choose two ability scores for your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/sorcerer#TOC-Bloodline\">bloodline</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/afflictions/poison\">poison</a>&nbsp;to affect.</p>\n<p>At 11th level, whenever you apply your progenitor’s sting to a weapon, you can magically apply it onto all willing allies’ weapons within 20 feet as well. This counts as one use of your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/sorcerer#TOC-Bloodline\">bloodline</a>&nbsp;ability.</p>",
